data.description: Welcome to your dream colonial-style townhome nestled in the charming Oak Springs neighborhood of Silver Spring, Maryland. This meticulously maintained property boasts a perfect blend of modern amenities and classic architectural charm. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior featuring all-new appliances, elegant quartz countertops, and a mosaic backsplash that adds a touch of sophistication to the kitchen. The breakfast bar, strategically placed for additional seating, seamlessly connects the kitchen to the open dining and living room– an ideal space for your lifestyle. This two-bedroom, two-full-bathroom home is a haven of comfort and convenience. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering not only ample closet space but also a sitting vanity. The attention to detail is evident throughout the property, from the tasteful finishes to the abundance of natural light that floods every room. The basement is complete with a washer/dryer for added convenience and opens up to a versatile family room – the perfect spot for movie nights or a home office. Extra storage space ensures that you have room for all your belongings without sacrificing style. Step outside to discover a fenced-in backyard the lush greenery and well-maintained landscaping create a serene atmosphere for enjoyment. One of the property's standout features is its proximity to the beautiful Good Hope Park, just a short stroll away. This scenic oasis offers multi-sport areas and a community center, providing the perfect setting for outdoor activities and community engagement. Commute with ease, as public transportation options are conveniently located nearby. The property's strategic location also grants you quick access to major thoroughfares such as ICC-200, North Hampshire Ave, and Route 29, connecting you effortlessly to the diverse amenities and attractions of the surrounding area. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
